# Array Searching 

Array is operation for finding index of given element

1. Linear Search

function linearSearch(arr , target){
	for(let i = 0 ; i < arr.length ; i++){
		if(arr[i] === target) return i	
	}
	return -1
}

time Complexity - O(n)

